Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:54.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:59.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:04.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止めるその全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:09.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:19.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:29.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていればいつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえばそれは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:39.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:54.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分は駄目だと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:59.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:04.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:10.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:54.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:59.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:04.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:09.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:19.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便为永不凋谢之花命名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:29.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:34.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:39.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:54.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:59.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:04.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:10.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.09,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.62,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くコノ手デ掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戻っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして今　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が分からなくてもいい　そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:35.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境なく燃える炎を　雲中が指を指す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:41.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと　強くなって　誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:49.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したい人の思い　闇をコノ手デ祓おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.09,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 我追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.62,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:55.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到原点也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨 只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:35.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 直冲云霄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:41.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强 保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:49.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人 亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.77,0:23:51.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次召集大家不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是为了揪出叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看见达摩大人好像在操纵火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道这次的事件是达摩大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更重要的是 他缺席这次会议不就是证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等天亮了我一定要去金刚深山找老爸问个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说今天明陀的干部聚集在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 有什么传言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所长刚才紧急召集了守卫深部的所有上级驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我们就猜是不是要开会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧急召集？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是现在放松对深部的警备是不是不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说得对 我去问问所长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所的钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他突然去外派所干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.65,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15\fad(0,517)\3c&HC4732D&\pos(352,605)}背信弃义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷静下来想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我太过在意要点燃蜡烛这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才会把整根蜡烛烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正要点着的是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.14,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:55.64,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.14,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说 只要一点火就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍微点一下就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 修拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我点着了 我完美地点着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于站上起跑线了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧 我还没起跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还必须能随心所欲地操控火焰才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的火焰要是再失控 可是会被当作驱除对象处死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就开门见山地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个恶魔是撒旦之子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如今也没什么好辩解的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你帮助藤本狮郎秘密把他抚养长大 有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了让他成为对抗撒旦的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在座的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不要和我打个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看看这个撒旦之子会成为虚无界的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是会成为骑士团… 不 物质界的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逮捕梅菲斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是否接受梅菲斯特·菲雷斯卿的赌约就用投票来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先 他必须通过半年后的驱魔师资格考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}另外 如果他被判断为对物质界有威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就要将其作为驱魔对象立刻处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 是啊 路还长着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是这对个人来说只是一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对于全人类来说却是一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么呢 先冷静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然是蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叛徒果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对护摩坛动手脚的也是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}审议会的时候你的言辞也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我平常虽然不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我觉得你比别人更为明陀着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可你为什么会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是为了让明陀的人清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正的叛徒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有日本支部长 梅菲斯特·菲雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特？ 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八年前 我刚进入驱魔塾的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老师告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宝生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这事你不要说出去 你知道不净王的左眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王的左眼是梅菲斯特·菲雷斯支部长的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被寄放在最深部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}据说还有一个右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但还是个谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是打倒不净王的明陀家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我以为你会知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}左眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还 还有这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 那其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老师一直对梅菲斯特的行动抱有怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以打算揭发他的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且老师还发现胜吕达摩也牵涉其中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因此我也开始协助藤堂老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这几年中彻底调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然一直没有查出决定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但一周前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在梵蒂冈举行的对梅菲斯特的惩戒审讯中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得到了十分确凿的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特没有杀死撒旦之子 还私自将其抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 为了让那个撒旦之子活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还使用了我们明陀的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道这意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是说胜吕达摩和梅菲斯特一起图谋不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正如藤堂老师所料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在这里哪有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这事总有一天会公之于众
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 婀蜜哩帝 吽 癹吒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的高层已经不能信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}右眼和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要由藤堂老师封印到比这里更安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少在大家面前公开把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩把明陀卖给了正十字骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而上面的人却还一心一意奉他为首领
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连父亲大人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对那些人我要说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩家不正是愚忠之首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论我说什么 他们都只会说「是你想多了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在是这样松懈的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开始得比想象更快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我这就让待机的上级驱魔师部队逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蟒也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮已经是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是认真的吗 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不需要你的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这都是为了拯救明陀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看在我们自幼相识的份上 就让我来超度你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 蝮 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们不要自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 好像在晃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所好像出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别忘了惩戒审讯时作出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没办法 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个晃动不是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是入侵者 快到深部去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}深部出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天花板正在被腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这只老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你欺骗蝮到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老狐狸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错 但是我这次只是协助一下宝生同学而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正如他所说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和藤堂老师没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你被骗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全被藤堂骗了啊 你知道吗 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被欺骗了的 是你们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道叛徒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然是蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安静 大家不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要重整态势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久不见了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙士 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鸡冠头很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然很想和你慢慢聊 但我得去追蝮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能不能放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去追蝮？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}归根结底 蝮的背叛和这里发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一切不都是你一手造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不参加会议去做什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说话啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像蝮说的那样 你背叛了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然这样 你就在大家面前把真相说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使你是我儿子也不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都这个时候了 你还在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之现在要快去追蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要听妈妈和老师的话 别惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别给我摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别总在这种时候摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我告诉你 你要是不说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今往后你就不是我爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开什么玩笑 你才不是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别在我面前摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是我的儿子 把他还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥 奥村…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是胜吕的爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样你就高兴了吗 你说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你 胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚 刚才是不是有什么闪了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然不太清楚具体发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我先告诉你 你以后一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了 向老爸道歉 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和你没关系吧 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要轻易和老爸断绝关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不想被你教训
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了好了 龙士和燐都别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在这里和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你爱去哪去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亏我以前还觉得你很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:35.99,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看错你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}青色的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我又不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 巴萨拉 叽尼 哈拉 涅哈他那 娑婆诃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 燐 给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我又不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜欢撒旦才当他儿子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟老爸道歉 等他死了可就晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在马上跟老爸道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉擅自插手 但请先逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特没有杀死撒旦之子 还私自将其抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这个孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到廉造的朋友竟然是撒旦之子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 嘛呢 叭哒 吽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:12.72,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}注：六字大明咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你忘记惩戒审讯时定下的条件了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放出火焰的话就会被当作驱魔对象处死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说很重要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别妨碍我 母猪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:55.47,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 佉契佉契 佉比契著央著 吒契婆那 娑婆诃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁来帮个忙把他隔离起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他已经晕过去了 没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所长 引起这么大的骚动真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件事你稍后应该会解释清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:06.42,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第五集 一缘一会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对你来说可能负担还是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}替我向燐问好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毒性更猛烈的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道藤堂的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放出火焰被大家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.03,0:24:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看着吧 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
